<item>
            <title>[SPARK-39915] Dataset.repartition(N) may not create N partitions</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-39915</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Looks like there is a behavior change in Dataset.repartition in 3.3.0. For example, `spark.range(10, 0).repartition(5).rdd.getNumPartitions` returns 5 in Spark 3.2.0, but 0 in Spark 3.3.0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13474077">SPARK-39915</key>
            <summary>Dataset.repartition(N) may not create N partitions</summary>
